<% content_for :head do %>
    <title>Panda Tickle: About the App</title>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "aboutapp", :media => "all" %>
<% end %>

<% content_for :center do %>
    <section id="mid_section">
    <h2><span class="head2">About the App</span></h2>
      <br>
    <p>This is a Edutainment application that uses the following;</p>
    <br>
    <ul id="tech_list">
      <li>HTML5, particularly canvas</li>
      <li>CSS3</li>
      <li>Sprite3D (JS API for 3D transforms)</li>
      <li>Javascript</li>
      <li>jQuery</li>
      <li>Ruby on Rails</li>
    </ul>
      <br>
    <p>The purpose of the application is to educate children about Pandas and conservation while also providing a fun
    and simple game for them to play.</p>
    <br>
    <h3><span class="head3">Features</span></h3>
      <br>
    <p>Below are two lists, on the left are current site features, on the right are features to come. Both these lists
    will be updated in the coming weeks. Also on the right you will see a twitter feed from my account, this will
    include updates on the application development for Panda Tickle and other projects I am working on at present.</p>
      <br>
    <table>
      <thead>
      <tr>
      <th>Current Features</th>
      <th>Pending Features</th>
      </tr>
      </thead>
      <tfoot>
      <tr></tr>
      </tfoot>
      <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>CSS 3D Animation on Home Page</td>
        <td>Make game playable on a mobile device</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Combination of CSS 3D and HTML5 canvas for game</td>
        <td>Make site design responsive</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Use of audio tags for game events</td>
        <td>Add more game controls eg mute button</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Post game scores</td>
        <td>Sign in with Facebook and Google+</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>CSS3 slide show, in Panda Facts</td>
        <td>Add game levels</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Sign in with your Twitter ID</td>
        <td>Add user feedback</td>
      </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    </section>
<% end %>

